  <title>Type Spanish language accents in Endless</title>

  <p>It's easy to type accents on Endless - it is the same as most other
  platforms. On a Spanish Latin American keyboard, start by pressing the accute
  accent key and then the letter you'd like to accent:</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>`</key><key>a</key></keyseq> = á</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>`</key><key>e</key></keyseq> = é</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>`</key><key>i</key></keyseq> = í</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>`</key><key>o</key></keyseq> = ó</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>`</key><key>u</key></keyseq> = ú</p>

  <p><keyseq><key>"</key><key>u</key></keyseq> = ü</p>
